data.title: “Freedom of Expression” International Cartoon Exhibition, Drøbak, Norway
data.meta_description: "Freedom of Expression" International Cartoon Exhibition, Drøbak, Norway, by Olivia Inkwell. Visit Olivia Inkwell's "Freedom of Expression" International
data.text:
The Norwegian Cartoonist Gallery (Avistegnernes Hus), 22nd of April at 14:00 till 21st of May 2017.

Per Edgard Kokkvold, Writer, and Chairman of the Norwegian Broadcasting Council. Former newspaper editor, secretary general of the Norwegian Press Association and leader of the Press Complaints Commission will be inaugurating the exhibition at 14.00 PM on 22nd April.

Photo from exhibition opening: https://www.facebook.com/347909365513/photos/?tab=album&album_id=10158522519535514
